Package: jrcgpt
Type: Package
Title: GPT API Client developed for JRC Infrastructure
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Guy", "Schvitz",
      email = "guy.schvitz@ec.europa.eu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Helper functions to interact with the GPT API infrastructure of the Joint Research Centre (JRC), including functions to start and update chat messages, send requests, and extract response content. While this package is designed for JRC's corporate GPT services, the functions may also work with other compatible GPT endpoints.
